{"tid":2359764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普川沒有輸！！","createTime":"2021-01-09T07:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T10:49:28.000Z","uid":210522,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a33d30fbde6b015dd3cc6c768dbf2522d8a91fe","tid":2359764,"uid":210522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"普川先生一直在對你們那些民主黨有利的大選中戰鬥<br />\n他是個有血有肉的總統，國會一直有議員戳他，被彭斯戳過的傷不能簡單治好，被拜登換掉的票數也無法恢復<br />\n跟奧巴馬，希拉莉，那些懦夫比起來，普川才是最厲害的！<br />\n他沒有讓任何人失望，他守住了第45任總統，守住了大家振興經濟的希望，普川才沒有輸！<br />\n就算大勢已定，他戰鬥到了最後，守護美國總統到最後，是你們連登仔燈輸了，普川先生才是勝者！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffedddab09b762356931410e276d987c5cc95c98","tid":2359764,"uid":294518,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"2017年川普剛上任不久，拉黑了幾個謾罵他及家人的推號，被告上巡迴法庭，敗訴。因為他的推號在總統期間屬於國家財產，謾罵、譏諷是屬於言論自由的範疇，應該保護，所以，總統川普無權拉黑任何人。<br />\n2021年1月9號，推特公司以川普的帳號有問題，強硬的封鎖了他的帳號，隨意的侵吞美國的國家財產，居然沒有任何事情。<br />\n當權力被邪惡掌控，法律、次序、道德，像一個面團，搓圓、按扁，都在權力方寸之間！"},{"pid":"28994f469ddc71642e6b2bebf31e3631bddfdf82","tid":2359764,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"撲街樓主，有畫面"},{"pid":"4d4532ee89e938b950ac867306bd6ed5de5951fe","tid":2359764,"uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"75秒解釋怎樣偷盜選舉&hellip;難以置信，但就這麼發生了!<br />\n75 seconds to explain how to steal an election...unbelievable, but it just happened!<br />\n<a href=\"https://gtv.org/getter/5ff92f0187fabe2daf33b37b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgtv.org%2Fgetter%2F5ff92f0187fabe2daf33b37b&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=2f906484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gtv.org/getter/5ff92f0187fabe2daf33b37b</a>"},{"pid":"19df30f34182b038c3bdcbb497def9b35d1a93ba","tid":2359764,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"這也太令人興奮了！xx黨靠刪帖、封號愚弄，統治牆國人民，今天它們的代理人也如法炮製，妄圖統治美國，美國人民手裡的槍桿子，會答應嗎？曾經的預言，終於變了殘酷的現實，降臨到川普總統和美國人民的頭上。它們如此瘋狂，才能讓川普總統徹底丟掉幻想：要不進監獄，要不滅掉背後黑手xx黨！"},{"pid":"e8d8f04bea259b0a5c9a310195064306a8eac4c0","tid":2359764,"uid":210522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28994f469ddc71642e6b2bebf31e3631bddfdf82","tid":2359764,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"撲街樓主，有畫面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"不要逃啊，卑鄙的拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453c6bd9bd31b66e58a288107269ccb9af4b8c7d","tid":2359764,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8d8f04bea259b0a5c9a310195064306a8eac4c0","tid":2359764,"uid":210522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28994f469ddc71642e6b2bebf31e3631bddfdf82","tid":2359764,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"撲街樓主，有畫面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"不要逃啊，卑鄙的拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:44:23.000Z","msg":"佢無逃喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c6b6e11e67873f2cddef1f60d8895d98783bcf","tid":2359764,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srNE3ya.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrNE3ya.jpg&h=a4d0d65a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9da0af8e451568bc576f2afdffb044054d9ee9c","tid":2359764,"uid":210522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453c6bd9bd31b66e58a288107269ccb9af4b8c7d","tid":2359764,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8d8f04bea259b0a5c9a310195064306a8eac4c0","tid":2359764,"uid":210522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28994f469ddc71642e6b2bebf31e3631bddfdf82","tid":235976